{"tid":2118471,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】台版Angelababy飯店渡假扮出國　黃琳泳池邊擺Pose好誘人","createTime":"2020-07-21T13:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T14:24:54.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"52b6b5ce3d456d6b6959dac0e26e8698019480f3","tid":2118471,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:08:46.000Z","msg":"因應疫情嚴重關係，許多國家同地區都沒有重新開放觀光旅遊，許多人只好想盡辦法在本土發掘好去處。而有台版Angelababy之稱的網紅黃琳就非常懂得吃喝玩樂，繼去完墾丁渡假扮美人魚之後，近日就去住飯店當出國旅遊，在台北福華大飯店享受同陽光玩遊戲，還一連擺出多個性感Pose，非常誘人。<br />\n<br />\n非常懂得利用飯店的環境當背景拍美照的黃琳，身穿碎花泳衣上陣大展傲人好身材。在飯店的淋浴間玩拍攝的她大擺誘人Pose，呈現冷酷女人一面，整個畫面十足像專業的雜誌拍攝。除此之外，當然少不了去飯店的泳池大玩特玩，而黃琳亦趁機曬長腿同陽光玩遊戲，還擺出一個呈S形曲線的Pose，還非常幽默自嘲：「膝蓋好痛。」一系列的美照看到不少網友目不轉睛。"},{"pid":"b50fd3e6b86becf325331b00f9773878a2e00d06","tid":2118471,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200704/356128505861378048.jpeg/SKL-u86qVCSJWwQAWkLkTiwkhoT8UA5kbjseEW47HhE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200704%2F356128505861378048.jpeg%2FSKL-u86qVCSJWwQAWkLkTiwkhoT8UA5kbjseEW47HhE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a10ecb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200721/362246202248531968.jpeg/79Am5kIeuWUhXWaC73dzZkorZ7pes1XsffKu333yrt8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200721%2F362246202248531968.jpeg%2F79Am5kIeuWUhXWaC73dzZkorZ7pes1XsffKu333yrt8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f4d185bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200721/362246930849468416.jpeg/DSV02rhaQDZOAK3R6kVfniCgYgWdKYOnrazJO62syTs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200721%2F362246930849468416.jpeg%2FDSV02rhaQDZOAK3R6kVfniCgYgWdKYOnrazJO62syTs%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f66d7bd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49522c723